  <section class="section pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>费用说明</h2>
        <p>费用以人民币计价，报名早鸟优惠截止至 2026年1月31日。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="price-card">
          <div class="price-title">行程费用</div>
          <div class="price-number">59,800 元/人</div>
          <div class="price-note">早鸟价：56,800 元/人（2026年1月31日前）</div>
        </div>
        <div class="price-card">
          <div class="price-title">费用包含</div>
          <ul class="price-list">
            <li>学习、座谈与交流活动费用</li>
            <li>场地租赁与专家讲座</li>
            <li>翻译、影像、公关费用与学习费用</li>
            <li>四星级酒店住宿（双床房，2人一间）</li>
            <li>全程商务用餐（早午晚）</li>
            <li>当地用车服务</li>
            <li>司机及导游小费</li>
            <li>个人海外人身意外保险</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="price-card">
          <div class="price-title">费用不包含</div>
          <ul class="price-list">
            <li>护照办理费用</li>
            <li>美国签证费</li>
            <li>往返美国机票</li>
            <li>单人住宿差价</li>
            <li>费用包含未列出的其他费用</li>
            <li>个人消费与额外小费</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <div class="cta-text">
          <h2>锁定席位，优先获取定制方案</h2>
          <p>名额有限，提交意向后即可进入名额锁定流程，并获取专属顾问沟通与城市资源清单。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a class="btn primary" href="#apply">立即报名</a>
          <a class="btn light" href="#contact">微信咨询</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section form" id="apply">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>报名表</h2>
        <p>填写信息后进入审核与名额锁定流程。我们将在 1-2 个工作日内联系你。</p>
      </div>
      <form class="apply-form" action="https://jsj.top/f/DTAFvG" method="get" target="_blank">
        <div class="form-grid">
          <label class="field">
            <span>姓名</span>
            <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="请输入姓名" required />
          </label>
          <label class="field">
            <span>律所</span>
            <input type="text" name="firm" placeholder="请输入律所名称" required />
          </label>
          <label class="field">
            <span>所在城市</span>
            <input type="text" name="city" placeholder="请输入城市" required />
          </label>
          <label class="field">
            <span>是否持有美国签证</span>
            <select name="visa" required>
              <option value="">请选择</option>
              <option value="yes">是</option>
              <option value="no">否</option>
              <option value="applying">办理中</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label class="field">
            <span>法律先生 VIP 会员</span>
            <select name="vip" required>
              <option value="">请选择</option>
              <option value="yes">是</option>
              <option value="no">否</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label class="field full">
            <span>希望了解美国的哪个内容？</span>
            <textarea name="interest" placeholder="如：AI 与法律、跨境投资、知识产权、美国律所合作等" rows="4"></textarea>
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="form-note">
          点击提交将跳转至金数据完成报名。提交即视为进入名额锁定流程，报名通过后将引导完成付费，以最终支付为准。
        </div>
        <div class="form-actions">
          <button class="btn primary" type="submit">提交报名</button>
          <button class="btn ghost" type="reset">清空重填</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-box">
        <div>
          <div class="contact-title">咨询与报名支持</div>
          <div class="contact-text">添加微信获取行程手册与顾问沟通</div>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-wechat">
          <div class="wechat-label">微信号</div>
          <div class="wechat-id">flxs33</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

