        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="footer-title">联系</div>
          <div class="footer-text">微信：flxs33</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="footer-title">声明</div>
          <div class="footer-text">页面内容为展示模板，实际行程以最终发布为准。</div>
